{"tid":1442214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下你地對峙嘅時候唔好剩係叫黑社會","createTime":"2019-08-11T01:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T01:43:15.000Z","uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bcb3925978c60948284979c4a590991c546731de","tid":1442214,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:15:12.000Z","msg":"重申返5大訴求 撤回啊 要俾鏡頭聽到我地講緊撤回<br />\n運動繼續失焦 狗方同政府就會不停將風向spin去<br />\n單純嘅警民衝突 慢慢支持我哋嘅人就會忘記初衷<br />\n而警民衝突並唔係個班人爭取嘅野嚟<br />\n再係咁會落入政府圈套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280c976067ace6e2a1b060a9ce80556ffb8a9789","tid":1442214,"uid":235021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:17:01.000Z","msg":"你上嚟帶頭"},{"pid":"559145b9a87da28520e10c360287c4843e7f121a","tid":1442214,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"280c976067ace6e2a1b060a9ce80556ffb8a9789","tid":1442214,"uid":235021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:17:01.000Z","msg":"你上嚟帶頭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:28:21.000Z","msg":"有嗌 太細聲無人理"},{"pid":"07898bf33c67d7b871ca80d8b0bd8877307c6e26","tid":1442214,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:29:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無差別襲擊製造恐怖氣氛已經係恐怖主義！我地係嘅係要為警隊嘅行為正名！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">警隊失控無差別襲擊，係屬於國家恐怖主義嘅行為，已經超越「過度暴力」、「濫捕」同「濫用暴力」，依啲字眼淡化佢嘅「拐帶」、「恐怖襲擊」等非法行為，警隊嘅行為喺好多國家已經係可以定義為失去合法性啲武裝組織。<br />\n警察喺民間嘅認受性極低，失去合法地執行職務嘅能力，街坊見到警察嘅武裝會產生恐懼感。恐怖主義管治已引起社會及國際極度不安。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-syd2-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/67762343_2365204796898460_5302639169934196736_o.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQmTQg6OhdO_6R-Rejb-Rq9c3XaVJ6vMCONG03O-sqe_h2s74zGuYzrB3jqj1EduBJo&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-syd2-1.xx&amp;oh=85645ceddaf282f8312a7106e366f0b0&amp;oe=5DDE6B2B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-syd2-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F67762343_2365204796898460_5302639169934196736_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQmTQg6OhdO_6R-Rejb-Rq9c3XaVJ6vMCONG03O-sqe_h2s74zGuYzrB3jqj1EduBJo%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-syd2-1.xx%26oh%3D85645ceddaf282f8312a7106e366f0b0%26oe%3D5DDE6B2B&h=61e168b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別化武襲擊！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[過期催淚彈][有圖] 毒到連眼都起水泡！！！！！麻煩全世界前線中線後線街坊啊婆啊伯！！戴靚少少既Gear唔該！！！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436725</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbU3GrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=696d89ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n已有<span style=\"color: orange;\">43,668</span>/100,000個簽名（11 Aug 2019 at 09:29）<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港警察 恐怖組織<br />\n過期化武 無差別襲擊<br />\nHKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!</span></span>"},{"pid":"0142922b0caaf525a00dfc439f7839e46813b3ec","tid":1442214,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:30:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">SET DEADLINE<br />\n</span></span><br />\n依家情況同上一個月差多<br />\n又係做好多嘢令到<span style=\"color: red;\">行動失去咗個目的</span><br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得 和理非&gt;deadline&gt;勇武升級 嘅抗爭概念<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1431556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1431556</a><br />\n<br />\n其實點解大家放棄左deadline?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1437366\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1437366</a><br />\n<br />\n本人草擬計劃（無共識，紅字字眼為我建議之重點）<br />\n「於824訂立18區游擊deadline<br />\n行動會無通知無預告日子於進行18區警署進行。<br />\n各位市民請盡量避免靠近警署，而亦注意到黑社會對市民之恐怖襲擊，請踴躍匯報，我們必<span style=\"color: red;\">不畏懼、不徇私、不對他人懷惡意，盡力保護市民身命及財產。</span><br />\n<br />\n1/9訂立大三罷deadline，<span style=\"color: red;\">正式宣布開啟臨時議會之準備</span>，只作通知，在一個月政府必須重拾市民對政府之信任，否則於1/10正式對外界宣傳香港政府因使用<span style=\"color: red;\">恐怖主義管治失去合法性及失去市民支持</span>：<br />\n-元朗黑社會勾結，及多次故意包庇恐怖份子無差別襲擊<br />\n-武裝警察向市民無差別襲擊，並非執法行動<br />\n-多次非法剝削市民人身自由，以執法或拘捕之名嚴重侵害人身安全及傷害他人身體<br />\n-多次<span style=\"color: red;\">故意違反合法使用氣化催淚神經毒劑指引</span>無必要起過量使用，於民居過量無差別無定向使用<span style=\"color: red;\">或產生高度毒性之過期化武</span>，此舉危險市民生命安全，以及製造之社會恐慌及不安，無疑為<span style=\"color: red;\">非法恐怖主義行為</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此恐怖主義管治已引起社會及國際極度不安，為平息社會不安，市民會成立臨時議會正式取代香港特區政府，為平息社會動盪，避免進一步經濟損失。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n預告8月尾一個星期會demostrate政府再無力管治及保護市民<br />\n為回復社會穩定及回復經濟，9月2大罷工晒馬，開始全力文宣討論成立臨時議會事項<br />\n一個月期限要求政府提出方案平息社會不安，否則會於10月1正式宣布取代特區政府"},{"pid":"dadf0bdc7b04c6c8d3b973a643f77f4377731c2c","tid":1442214,"uid":235021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"559145b9a87da28520e10c360287c4843e7f121a","tid":1442214,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"280c976067ace6e2a1b060a9ce8055